{"tid":1892364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人咁辛苦，點解仲要生仔","createTime":"2020-02-22T12:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T13:02:39.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3f10ab6dcad2823cbb99aeb8fd727435344912","tid":1892364,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"仲要扮到好似為佢好咁<br />\n帶佢黎到世上<br />\n做咩都冇自由<br />\n唔啱就打鬧<br />\n講到好似一切為佢好咁<br />\n學呢樣學個樣<br />\n到頭來<br />\n講到底<br />\n就係唔想衰俾人睇<br />\n係自己唔想衰俾人睇<br />\n根本呢個世界<br />\n太虛偽<br />\n同養貓狗一樣<br />\n講到為佢好<br />\n又困住佢<br />\n吠又電鳩佢<br />\n瀨尿又打鳩佢<br />\n聽話個陣<br />\n俾其他狗主讚個陣<br />\n就講成自己教得好功勞<br />\n人始終都係虛偽<br />\n講真<br />\n其實做人本身<br />\n已經痛苦<br />\n為呢種痛苦<br />\n再加添痛苦<br />\n係人世間虛偽<br />\n人生在世<br />\n已經冇太多野可以講<br />\n芸芸眾生<br />\n其實每人都好似狗咁<br />\n自生自滅<br />\n有d好命d<br />\n有d冇咁好命<br />\n只有被屠宰既份<br />\n從來冇黎過世上<br />\n就最好"},{"pid":"29748186dd237367e2745e94f34d11c532c68689","tid":1892364,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"唔好以為改咗名就唔認得你。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>黃藍Youtube資料庫，持續更新中：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2SRSfxu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SRSfxu&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=2d5058e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2SRSfxu</a><br />\n專注YouTube戰線嘅IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/?hl=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellowyoutubehk%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-tw&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=45cd8d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/?hl=zh-tw</a></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"655001eaee653a6e6f3ab211beda6b00e2585415","tid":1892364,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"傳宗接代"}]}